                    p
                        | I am a 4A Computer Science student from University of Waterloo. I am an iOS developer, technology lover, half marathon runner and German learner.
                .col-md-4.text-center
                    img#me(src='dist/img/steven.png', alt='Steven Xu')
                .col-md-4
                    h3 Details
                    p
                        strong Name:
                    p Wen (Steven) Xu
                    p
                        strong Age:
                    p 22
                    p
                        strong Favorite Food:
                    p Beef noodle soup

